<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Transcribe without typing.</h1>

  <p>Let the computer transcribe the text and you just correct the mistakes.</p>

  <p class="actions">
    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large fileinput-button">
      <%= icon('upload-alt') %> &nbsp;
      Upload a File

      <input id="fileupload" type="file" name="recording[original_audio_file]"
             data-url="<%= url_for(@recording) %>">
    </a>

    <small id="url_toggle">or <%= link_to "Enter URL", '#' %></small>

    <%= form_for(@recording, html: { class: 'url_upload hide form-horizontal' }) do |f| %>
      <%= f.text_field :url, placeholder: 'http://', class: 'url' %>
      <%= f.submit 'Go', class: 'btn' %>
    <% end %>

    <div id="progress" class="progress progress-success progress-striped hide">
        <div class="bar"></div>
    </div>

  </p>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid features">
  <div class="span1">&nbsp;</div>

  <div class="span5">
    <h3> <%= icon('desktop') %> &nbsp; Computers + Humans = Win!</h3>

    <p>
      Transcribing is a tedious and work-intensive task.<br />
      Most people hate to do it.
    </p>

    <p>Computers don't mind doing it, but they make mistakes.</p>

    <p>
      We want to make it more fun, by letting the computer do the heavy&#8209;lifting
      while you just correct the mistakes.<br />
    </p>

    <p>This way you train the computer to recognize words better.<br />
      <%= link_to "Learn more",  { action: :about } %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="span5">
    <h3> <%= icon('code-fork') %> &nbsp; It's Open-Source and Shared</h3>

    <p>
      Our project is free and open-source.
    </p>

    <p>We aim to improve open and free speech recognition.</p>

    <p>Every transcription you make is shared with the community.<br />
      <%= link_to "Learn more",  { action: :about } %>
    </p>

    <p>
      If you're interested in contributing, checkout our <br />
      <%= link_to "GitHub repository", "http://www.github.com/skpvox/live_transcriber" %>
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="span1">&nbsp;</div>
</div>

<div class="section">

  <div class="section-header">
    <h1>The power of collaboration.</h1>
    <!-- TODO: This doesn't sound quite right yet. Improve it! -->
    <p class="lead">If 5,000 people help just 10 minutes we could transcribe over 1 month in a single day.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="span4 statistics nowrap">
      <div class="number"><%= icon(:time)%> <%= distance_of_time_in_words( Transcription.today.sum(:duration) ) %></div>
      <div class="desc">Transcribed Today</div>
    </div>

    <div class="span4 statistics nowrap">
      <div class="number"><%= icon(:time)%> <%= distance_of_time_in_words( ReviewedTranscription.today.sum(:duration) ) %></div>
      <div class="desc">Reviewed Today</div>
    </div>

    <div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>

  </div>

</div>
